tar -cf etc-backup.tar etc 
tar -tvf etc-backup.tar (look into a tar file)
tar -tvf etc-backup.tar | wc -l (count the lines)

 
tar -xf etc-backup.tar- extract a tar file
tar -xvf etc-backup.tar- extract a tar file with verbose
gzip etc_backup.tar - zip a file
gunzip etc_backup.tar.gz - unzip a file
tar -czf etc-backup.tar.gz etc - create a tar and zip it
ls -lh - list the size of a file
